Building & installing
---------------------

From fMBT sources you can build a normal version, and a low-dependency
"Android" version.

Normal version dependencies:
        glib-2.0, boost (regex), libedit, cpp,
        python2.6+, python-pexpect, python-dbus

"Android" version dependencies:
        libedit

./autogen.sh # needed if working on sources from git repo
./configure
make
make install


Testing
-------

make check
        Tests the source tree.

test/git-HEAD/run.sh
        Test the latest commit in the current git branch.


Documentation
-------------

Start with doc/tutorial.txt and doc/overview.txt.
